{"tid":1389562,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"所有驚罷工/集會既公務員同我入黎","createTime":"2019-07-31T02:31:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T17:08:11.000Z","uid":41411,"like":124,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"adb6f0bb89db0296ef73049245092c58ba137310","tid":1389562,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T02:31:17.000Z","msg":"我自己都係一個公務員 知道公務員文化有幾濕鳩<br />\n但係大事大飛之下 我地絕對要企出黎表態<br />\n當成班細路企係前線面對住槍，棍，暴動罪等等<br />\n我地罷一日工算得Ｄ咩？如果你話驚因為咁比人炒<br />\n放心！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">公務員係絕對有權利去罷工，集會！</span><br />\n<br />\n下面係2006年既一份立法會文件 清楚講左公務員係有權利去參與罷工及集會<br />\n而係第6點亦都清楚講左唔可以因為罷工而炒我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AVwa6DZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAVwa6DZ.png&h=be072c14&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rqO5a5E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrqO5a5E.png&h=647487aa&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zAo5a5E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzAo5a5E.png&h=4865af4b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>我地首先係一個公民，然後先係一個公務員！</strong></span>"},{"pid":"2c14a3c41ab9996551ae85f44612e59562f0879f","tid":1389562,"uid":146737,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T02:33:51.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n自推<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3NYpocN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3NYpocN.jpg&h=e3874881&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mDfZZJj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmDfZZJj.jpg&h=ea72dfb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0MokFZw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0MokFZw.jpg&h=ffb7c73a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【文宣圖記錄版】反對逃犯條例修訂事件簿<br />\n<a href=\"https:/